      <title>대법 “지귀연 한두 잔 먹고 떠난 술자리, 동석자가 170만원 결제”</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/court_law/2025/10/20/XJAIEHCHKNHZBMUMXOPT32KMBI/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/court_law/2025/10/20/XJAIEHCHKNHZBMUMXOPT32KMBI/</guid>
